Title, Axis Labels & Limits

ggplot(data = mtcarz) + 
  geom_point(aes(x = disp, y = mpg), color = "blue") +
  labs(title = "mpg vs disp", x = "Displacement", y = "Miles Per Gallon")

Title

ggplot(data = mtcarz) + 
  geom_point(aes(x = disp, y = mpg), color = "blue") +
  ggtitle("mpg vs disp") + xlab("Displacement") + ylab("Miles Per Gallon")
